Watch Andrew Grimshawâ€™s presentation on Lancium below, and browse <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLIeB7asuU4W5ES_haPZl63EVWhj4TA2F_">all of the talks from day three</a> on YouTube.</p>

